OL,3,CThousands of civil servants to leave
OL,4,CLondon as Government cuts costs
OL,6,FThousands more civil servants are set
OL,7,Fto be moved out of London as the
OL,8,FGovernment seeks to cut costs and
OL,9,F"radically reform the state".
OL,11,FUnder plans announced on Wednesday,
OL,12,Fthe Government will cut the number of
OL,13,Fcivil servants working in London by
OL,14,F12,000 and shift jobs to a series of
OL,15,Fnew regional "campuses" across the
OL,16,Fcountry.
