OL,3,CThousands of civil servants to leave
OL,4,CLondon as Government cuts costs
OL,6,FThe changes will also see 11
OL,7,FGovernment office buildings in London
OL,8,Fclose, including one of its largest
OL,9,FWestminster sites, in a move expected
OL,10,Fto save #94 million a year by 2032.
OL,12,FPat McFadden, the Chancellor of the
OL,13,FDuchy of Lancaster, said the
OL,14,FGovernment was "taking more decision-
OL,15,Fmaking out of Whitehall and moving it
OL,16,Fcloser to communities all across the
OL,17,FUK".
