OL,3,CThousands of civil servants to leave
OL,4,CLondon as Government cuts costs
OL,6,FGovernment departments will be
OL,7,Fexpected to submit plans for
OL,8,Frelocating staff, including senior
OL,9,Fcivil servants, as part of the
OL,10,Fspending review due to be completed on
OL,11,FJune 11.
OL,13,FThe move will see two new major
OL,14,F"campuses" created, one in Manchester
OL,15,Ffocused on digital innovation and AI
OL,16,Fand another in Aberdeen on energy.
OL,18,FManchester is already home to major
OL,19,Foffices of the science and culture
OL,20,Fdepartments, while Aberdeen houses the
OL,21,Fnew Great British Energy headquarters.
