OL,6,FOther roles will be created in
OL,7,FBirmingham, Leeds, Cardiff, Glasgow,
OL,8,FDarlington, Newcastle and Tyneside,
OL,9,FSheffield, Bristol, Edinburgh, Belfast
OL,10,Fand York, with the changes expected to
OL,11,Fbring #729 million to the local
OL,12,Feconomy by 2030.
OL,14,FAmong the offices being closed in
OL,15,FLondon is 102 Petty France, one of the
OL,16,Flargest Government offices in the
OL,17,Fcapital and home to around 7,000 civil
OL,18,Fservants in the Ministry of Justice,
OL,19,FHM Courts and Tribunal Service, Crown
OL,20,FProsecution Service and the Government
OL,21,FLegal Department.
