OL,6,FThe Government will also close 39
OL,7,FVictoria Street, which has been home
OL,8,Fto the Department of Health and Social
OL,9,FCare since the end of 2017.
OL,11,FMr McFadden said: "By relocating
OL,12,Fthousands of Civil Service roles, we
OL,13,Fwill not only save taxpayers money, we
OL,14,Fwill make this Government one that
OL,15,Fbetter reflects the country it serves.
OL,17,F"We will also be making sure that
OL,18,FGovernment jobs support economic
OL,19,Fgrowth throughout the country.
