OL,3,CThousands of civil servants to leave
OL,4,CLondon as Government cuts costs
OL,6,F"As we radically reform the state, we
OL,7,Fare going to make it much easier for
OL,8,Ftalented people everywhere to join the
OL,9,FCivil Service and help us rebuild
OL,10,FBritain."
OL,12,FAround 80% of civil servants ` more
OL,13,Fthan 400,000 people ` already work
OL,14,Foutside London, but the most senior
OL,15,Fmandarins tend to be based in the
OL,16,Fcapital.
OL,18,FUnder Wednesday's proposals, half of
OL,19,Fsenior civil service roles would be
OL,20,Fbased outside London by 2030.
