OL,6,FProspect union general secretary Mike
OL,7,FClancy welcomed the plans to "increase
OL,8,Fand empower" civil servants based
OL,9,Foutside London, but called for more
OL,10,Fclarity on the role of arm's-length
OL,11,Fbodies outside the capital.
OL,13,FHe added: "We have been here before
OL,14,Fwith similar announcements, if this
OL,15,Fone is to be different, Government
OL,16,Fneeds to work closely with unions both
OL,17,Fon specific relocation plans and on
OL,18,Fthe wider Civil Service reform agenda."
